title: Top 101 free agents
itunes:title: Top 101 free agents
description:
A room filled with heroes -- Dan Hanzus, Gregg Rosenthal, Chris Wesseling and Marc Sessler -- discuss Adrian Peterson's lifted suspension, Peyton Manning's contract situation and more news around the NFL. The guys also break down the annual "Top 101 free agents" list.
